title: Franchise Hockey Manager 1.0.0 - 1.6.2 Patch - SoN
description:
Game: Franchise Hockey Manager
Version: 1.0.0 - 1.6.2
Coded: March 13, 2014 by SoN
Type: Patch

Description: Franchise Hockey Manager ("FHM") is the deepest, most immersive, and most customizable hockey management game in the world. Choose one of 19 leagues and select a team to guide to glory. Sign free agents, trade players, draft the next crop of superstars, and much more!

Instructions: This is just a basic patch. Install any version of FHM 1.0.0 through 1.6.2 as normal. Open the patch as admin. Click the "Browse For Exe" button and select fhm2014.exe from the installation folder. Tick the "Make Backup" box if you want to make a backup of the original exe. Click the "Crack Game" button. Open the game and register with the serial key "FHM2014-MWWF-WVTK-PN95-LXQ7-H665". That is it. Enjoy!
